title: Master ISDD fiches
text:
In this website, I’ll present various topics that were covered during my Master Bio-Informatics: In Silico Drug Design at the Université Paris-Cité.
This is not professional content so if you see that something isn’t right and would like to volunteer, please contact me at this address: martin.bari-garnier@etu.unistra.fr. Enjoy !
